javax.net.ssl.SSLHandshakeException: Received fatal alert: illegal_parameter 

Multiple customers reporting the issue with java based application connecting to Akamai. 

 

Sample Host:  [signin.coxautoinc.com|https://signin.coxautoinc.com/]  (Customer has currently dekamaized)

 

They were able to replicate on sappr.signin.coxautoinc.com (Connecting to 23.192.230.150 and 23.192.230.151)

Check tcp.stream eq 14 on ghostip-23.221.51.23_eth0-1773933750.pcap  for the error instance. 

Check tcp.stream eq 7 on ghostip-23.221.51.22_eth0-1773933029.pcap  for instance without the  illegal_parameter  error. 

